RIGHT, OKAY, UM,
HOW LONG DO YOU THINK...?

12:45.295 --> 12:48.168
I MEAN, JUST TECHNICALLY,
I'M OFF AT 6:00.

12:48.168 --> 12:49.539
AM I INVITED?

12:49.539 --> 12:51.171
EXCUSE ME?

12:51.171 --> 12:52.302
AM I INVITED
TO THE PARTY?

12:52.302 --> 12:53.904
OH.

12:53.904 --> 12:56.476
WELL, YEAH.
YES, YEAH, OF COURSE.

13:00.180 --> 13:03.213
WHAT WAS I SUPPOSED
TO SAY?

13:03.213 --> 13:04.484
UGH!

13:07.057 --> 13:10.220
OKAY, YEAH, GREAT.
ALL RIGHT, 14 CASES.

13:10.220 --> 13:11.361
[ PAGER BEEPING ]

13:11.361 --> 13:15.295
WHAT KIND? I DON'T KNOW.
MAYBE AN ASSORTMENT.

13:15.295 --> 13:17.327
MICROBREWS -- LOCALS.

13:17.327 --> 13:20.300
MAKE SURE THEY THROW IN
SOME BAR NUTS.

13:20.300 --> 13:22.402
I'M ORDERING
OFFICE SUPPLIES.

13:22.402 --> 13:24.204
OH, YEAH, SURE.

13:24.204 --> 13:26.877
MICROBREWS -- LOCAL.
AND THROW IN SOME BAR NUTS.

13:26.877 --> 13:29.079
7:00 WOULD BE BETTER
THAN 5:00.

13:29.079 --> 13:30.180
HEY, ANY LUCK?

13:30.180 --> 13:33.183
HEY, IF I DO, WILL YOU INVITE ME
TO THE PARTY?

13:33.183 --> 13:34.344
[ LAUGHS ]

13:34.344 --> 13:35.485
[ JERRY YELLS ]

13:35.485 --> 13:37.317
YEAH, GREAT.
OKAY, THANKS.

13:37.317 --> 13:38.849
TAKE IT EASY.

13:38.849 --> 13:39.850
MR. FROST.

13:39.850 --> 13:41.121
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?!

13:41.121 --> 13:43.353
WE'RE GOING TO TAKE CARE OF YOU,
ALL RIGHT?

13:43.353 --> 13:45.896
WHERE THE HELL
HAVE YOU BEEN?!

13:48.428 --> 13:50.901
WHEN I TELL YOU
TO START A CENTRAL LINE,

13:50.901 --> 13:53.603
YOU START A CENTRAL LINE --
NO JUDGMENT, NO QUESTION.

13:53.603 --> 13:57.167
GUY'S BEEN IN SEVEN HOSPITALS
IN THE LAST FOUR MONTHS.

13:57.167 --> 13:59.339
THE PATIENT
HAS A THREE-LUMBAR FUSION.

13:59.339 --> 14:01.471
HE'S A JUNKIE.
WE SHOULDN'T BE GIVING HIM --

14:01.471 --> 14:03.974
YEAH, HE'S AN ADDICT,
BUT HIS PAIN IS REAL.

14:03.974 --> 14:06.846
LOSE THE ATTITUDE, GET DOWN
THERE, START A CENTRAL LINE.

14:16.356 --> 14:19.289
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

14:23.994 --> 14:28.368
TOLD ME I HAD
A TOWEL INSIDE ME.

14:28.368 --> 14:29.940
WHO TOLD YOU THAT?

14:29.940 --> 14:34.604
A SURGEON --
AN OLDER MAN.

14:34.604 --> 14:35.605
HANDSOME.

14:35.605 --> 14:37.978
THAT'S DR. WEBBER.

14:37.978 --> 14:39.379
HE'S OUR CHIEF.

14:39.379 --> 14:40.580
YEAH.

14:40.580 --> 14:46.987
IT WAS A TOWEL THAT
SOMEBODY LEFT THE LAST TIME.

14:46.987 --> 14:48.358
YES, MA'AM.

14:48.358 --> 14:50.320
WHO WOULD DO THAT?

14:53.293 --> 14:56.466
THAT DOESN'T SEEM RIGHT,
DOES IT?

14:59.269 --> 15:02.973
NO, MA'AM, NO.
IT DOESN'T.

15:02.973 --> 15:07.437
I WAS WALKING AROUND
WITH A TOWEL INSIDE OF ME.

15:07.437 --> 15:10.480
HOW COULD THAT HAPPEN?

15:49.179 --> 15:52.582
SO? WHAT HAPPENS NOW?

15:57.287 --> 16:01.091
NOW YOU KEEP THIS TO YOURSELF
WHILE WE WORK IT OUT.

16:02.632 --> 16:04.464
DO THIS FOR ME.

16:04.464 --> 16:07.197
Man:
DR. STEVENS, CALL CCU.

16:07.197 --> 16:09.099
DR. STEVENS, CALL CCU.

16:11.201 --> 16:13.143
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

16:15.105 --> 16:17.347
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

16:20.280 --> 16:21.281
YOU OKAY?

16:21.281 --> 16:22.652
YEAH, YEAH, I'M GOOD.

16:22.652 --> 16:25.415
ARE YOU SURE?
BECAUSE YOU SEEM NOT OKAY.

16:25.415 --> 16:27.157
I'M FINE.
CABG WAS LONG.

16:27.157 --> 16:29.319
WELL, LET ME TAKE YOU
OUT TO DINNER TONIGHT.

16:29.319 --> 16:30.660
YOU CAN TELL ME
ALL ABOUT IT.

16:30.660 --> 16:33.363
REAL FOOD, WAITERS,
BIG CHUNKS OF CARBS IN A BASKET.

16:33.363 --> 16:34.524
I CAN'T.

16:34.524 --> 16:35.425
FORGET THE PARTY.

16:35.425 --> 16:37.497
YOU KNOW ABOUT THE PARTY?

16:37.497 --> 16:39.229
YOUR FRIENDS WILL BE
AT THE PARTY.

16:39.229 --> 16:41.131
YOU AND I CAN BE ALONE
SOMEWHERE ELSE.

16:41.131 --> 16:43.473
THANKS FOR NOT INVITING ME,
BY THE WAY. THAT FELT GOOD.

16:43.473 --> 16:46.206
DINNER -- THINK ABOUT DINNER.
PERFECT OPPORTUNITY.

16:46.206 --> 16:47.277
WELL...

16:47.277 --> 16:48.508
[ PAGER BEEPING ]

16:48.508 --> 16:49.509
UGH!

16:51.381 --> 16:53.383
STARTED HAVING SWELLING
OVER HER STERNUM,

16:53.383 --> 16:55.014
THEN BLOOD STARTED GUSHING.

16:55.014 --> 16:56.346
DR. BURKE IS ON HIS WAY.

16:56.346 --> 16:57.517
IS SHE DYING?

16:57.517 --> 16:59.419
SOMEBODY GET HIM OUT OF HERE.

16:59.419 --> 17:00.720
KEEP APPLYING PRESSURE.

17:00.720 --> 17:02.252
TYLER, CALL FOR AN O.R.

17:02.252 --> 17:04.254
WHAT THE HELL HAPPENED?
SHE GOT HER PROTAMINE?

17:04.254 --> 17:05.425
PER PROTOCOL.

17:05.425 --> 17:09.129
NO ALLERGIC, ANAPHYLACTIC,
OR HISTAMINE RESPONSES.

17:09.129 --> 17:10.430
HER LAST COUNTS?

17:10.430 --> 17:13.703
B.T., P.T.T., I.N.R.,
PLATELET COUNTS WERE ALL STABLE.

17:13.703 --> 17:15.535
EVEN HER H.N.H.
WERE STABLE.

17:15.535 --> 17:18.538
WHAT THE HELL WENT WRONG?
LET'S MOVE.

17:18.538 --> 17:20.670
HOLD ON.

17:22.172 --> 17:24.414
I POPPED A GLOVE.
WHAT?

17:24.414 --> 17:26.576
IN SURGERY,
WHEN I WAS HOLDING IT,

17:26.576 --> 17:28.578
I POPPED A GLOVE
WITH MY FINGERNAIL.

17:28.578 --> 17:30.480
I THINK I MAY HAVE NICKED
HER HEART.

17:30.480 --> 17:32.522
LET'S GO, PEOPLE.

17:44.394 --> 17:46.466
WHAT WERE YOU
THINKING ABOUT?

17:46.466 --> 17:48.768
YOU HAD EVERY OPPORTUNITY
TO SPEAK UP

17:48.768 --> 17:50.470
BEFORE I CLOSED HER CHEST.

17:50.470 --> 17:51.601
I'M SORRY.

17:51.601 --> 17:53.743
AND THEN YOU CONFESS
IN FRONT OF HER HUSBAND?

17:53.743 --> 17:55.775
YOU DON'T EVEN KNOW
IF YOU WERE THE CAUSE.

17:55.775 --> 17:57.447
YOU HAVE NO IDEA.

17:57.447 --> 17:58.748
I'M SORRY.

17:58.748 --> 18:00.380
SPONGE.

18:01.381 --> 18:02.412
THERE.

18:04.414 --> 18:06.216
OVER HERE.

18:06.216 --> 18:09.589
THERE.
LOOK AT THE WALL RUPTURE.

18:09.589 --> 18:11.821
IT'S A HELL OF A LOT MORE
THAN A FINGERNAIL.

18:11.821 --> 18:15.825
HER VENTRICULAR WALLS
ARE WEAK.

18:15.825 --> 18:18.868
I JUST HAD A CONVERSATION
WITH MR. PATTERSON.

18:18.868 --> 18:22.432
I WANT COPIES OF HIS WIFE'S
CHART IN MY OFFICE BY 5:00.

18:22.432 --> 18:25.505
TOMORROW, THE TWO OF YOU ARE
GOING TO MEET WITH ME AND LEGAL,

18:25.505 --> 18:30.480
AND YOU BETTER DAMN WELL BE ABLE
TO EXPLAIN WHAT HAPPENED HERE.

18:30.480 --> 18:33.783
PEOPLE POKING HOLES IN HEARTS
AND LEAVING TOWELS.

18:33.783 --> 18:37.487
YOU'RE GONNA GO BACK
AND TALK TO THE HUSBAND.

18:37.487 --> 18:39.319
REVIEW THE HISTORY.

18:39.319 --> 18:41.651
APOLOGIZE PROFUSELY.

18:41.651 --> 18:45.195
DR. GREY.

18:48.558 --> 18:50.530
YOU GOT CALLED
BEFORE THE CHIEF?

18:50.530 --> 18:51.631
TOMORROW MORNING.

18:51.631 --> 18:53.633
I COULD GET KICKED OUT
OF THE PROGRAM.

18:53.633 --> 18:54.804
I COULD, RIGHT?

18:54.804 --> 18:56.736
YOU'RE NOT GETTING
KICKED OUT.

18:56.736 --> 18:58.908
PATTERSON'S
JUST GONNA SUE.

18:58.908 --> 19:01.741
PATTERSON IS NOT GOING TO SUE.
YOU'RE NOT GETTING KICKED OUT.

19:01.741 --> 19:04.174
WHAT WERE YOU THINKING?
TELLING BURKE? SO STUPID.

19:04.174 --> 19:05.345
I TOLD HER NOT TO.

19:05.345 --> 19:06.416
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

19:06.416 --> 19:08.778
I GOT TO TAKE THIS.

19:08.778 --> 19:11.521
THANKS. THANK YOU.
VERY COMFORTING.

19:11.521 --> 19:13.653
I'LL WATCH YOUR BOOKS.

19:13.653 --> 19:14.724
OH.

19:14.724 --> 19:17.557
OKAY, SO THE BEER
IS COMING AT 7:00,

19:17.557 --> 19:20.630
AND SOME OF THE FLOOR NURSES
ARE BRINGING WINE.

19:20.630 --> 19:22.492
YOU INVITED NURSES?

19:22.492 --> 19:24.194
DID YOU CLEAR THIS
WITH MEREDITH?

19:24.194 --> 19:26.196
A FEW MORE PEOPLE
ISN'T GONNA MAKE A DIFFERENCE.

19:26.196 --> 19:27.397
A PARTY IS A PARTY.

19:27.397 --> 19:30.470
AND THE BIGGER THE PARTY,
THE LESS TIME FOR BAD SEX.

19:30.470 --> 19:31.841
WOULD YOU STOP SAYING THAT.

19:31.841 --> 19:34.444
HANK AND I HAVE GREAT SEX --
ALL THE TIME.

19:34.444 --> 19:37.607
WE'LL PROBABLY HAVE SEX AFTER
THE PARTY, OR DURING THE PARTY.

19:37.607 --> 19:39.909
AS LONG AS YOU CLEAR IT
WITH MEREDITH.

19:39.909 --> 19:43.553
HANK JUST NEEDS TO REALIZE
THAT DOCTORS CAN HAVE FUN.

19:43.553 --> 19:46.516
WE'RE NOT ALL WORKAHOLICS
WITH GOD COMPLEXES.

19:46.516 --> 19:49.419
WE ARE WORKAHOLICS
WITH GOD COMPLEXES.

19:53.793 --> 19:56.766
AND THE NOTARY CAN BE THERE
AT 6:30, TOO?

19:56.766 --> 19:59.529
AND THE HOME'S PHYSICIAN
WILL BE THERE

19:59.529 --> 20:02.502
TO ATTEST
TO HER MENTAL COMPETENCY?

20:02.502 --> 20:04.504
OKAY.

20:04.504 --> 20:07.777
IS THERE ANYTHING ELSE I NEED
TO BRING BESIDE MY LICENSE?

20:07.777 --> 20:10.380
AND MY CHECKBOOK.

20:10.380 --> 20:13.343
6:30 -- I'LL BE THERE.

20:13.343 --> 20:14.584
I HEARD.

20:14.584 --> 20:17.617
IT'S A NOTARY THING --
A THING TO GET NOTARIZED.

20:17.617 --> 20:19.449
I'M TALKING ABOUT
THE HEART THING.

20:19.449 --> 20:21.451
DO YOU WANT TO TALK
ABOUT IT?

20:21.451 --> 20:23.553
WE'RE ADULTS.

20:23.553 --> 20:26.296
WHEN DID THAT HAPPEN?

20:27.857 --> 20:30.830
AND HOW DO WE
MAKE IT STOP?

20:46.015 --> 20:47.677
DR. YANG.

20:47.677 --> 20:50.280
DR. BURKE.

20:51.781 --> 20:54.384
THAT BYPASS GRAFT
GOT A LITTLE COMPLICATED.

20:54.384 --> 20:56.656
IT'S NOTHING
I COULDN'T HANDLE.

20:56.656 --> 20:58.758
GOOD.

21:06.536 --> 21:08.998
UH-HUH.

21:08.998 --> 21:11.040
YEAH.

21:11.040 --> 21:12.642
MM-HMM.

21:14.644 --> 21:17.276
LISTEN,
I'LL CALL YOU BACK.

21:17.276 --> 21:19.479
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

21:19.479 --> 21:20.710
THAT WAS MY LAWYER.

21:20.710 --> 21:22.912
HE'S ADVISING ME
NOT TO TALK TO YOU.

21:22.912 --> 21:26.656
MR. PATTERSON, I KNOW THAT
YOU'RE FRUSTRATED AND ANGRY,

21:26.656 --> 21:27.987
BUT I NEED --

21:27.987 --> 21:30.960
ABOUT YOUR WIFE.

21:30.960 --> 21:33.292
THE WALLS OF HER HEART
ARE ABNORMALLY THIN.

21:33.292 --> 21:35.595
HEY, DON'T BLAME THIS
ON MY WIFE.

21:35.595 --> 21:38.297
I HEARD FROM YOUR VERY MOUTH
WHAT HAPPENED. I KNOW.

21:38.297 --> 21:39.569
BUT WE CAN'T TREAT HER.

21:39.569 --> 21:41.671
NO, SHE WAS IN THE BEST SHAPE
OF HER LIFE.

21:41.671 --> 21:44.534
YOU ASK HER CARDIOLOGIST.
SHE HAD LOST 100 POUNDS.

21:44.534 --> 21:46.806
DON'T YOU DARE
TRY TO HANG THIS ON HER.

21:46.806 --> 21:48.378
MR. PATTERSON, PLEASE.

21:48.378 --> 21:50.380
WE'RE THROUGH TALKING.

21:50.380 --> 21:52.712
[ SIGHS ]

22:15.865 --> 22:18.968
YOU DON'T LIKE ME VERY MUCH,
DO YOU?

22:18.968 --> 22:21.911
OH, JERRY,
IT'S NOT YOU SPECIFICALLY.

22:21.911 --> 22:24.914
IT'S JUST PEOPLE LIKE YOU,
THAT'S ALL.

22:24.914 --> 22:27.577
DOC,
I'M FEELING PRETTY GOOD.

22:27.577 --> 22:29.379
PAIN'S ABOUT A 3.

22:29.379 --> 22:31.381
A 3?
THAT'S EXCELLENT.

22:31.381 --> 22:33.383
MR. FROST, I'M GLAD
WE COULD HELP YOU OUT,

22:33.383 --> 22:35.555
AS WELL AS COUNTY,
MERCY WEST, SEATTLE PRES.

22:35.555 --> 22:38.057
A LOT OF PEOPLE HAVE
HELPED YOU OUT LATELY, JERRY.

22:38.057 --> 22:39.929
WE'RE PLEASED
WE COULD DO OUR PART.

22:39.929 --> 22:41.861
WHO'S ON DISCHARGE TODAY,
DR. KAREV?

22:41.861 --> 22:42.892
IZZIE STEVENS.

22:42.892 --> 22:45.765
DR. STEVENS IS GONNA
DISCHARGE YOU.

22:45.765 --> 22:47.937
WHOA, YOU CAN'T DISCHARGE ME.
I'M IN PAIN.

22:47.937 --> 22:49.899
YOU WERE IN PAIN.
NOW YOU'RE NOT.

22:49.899 --> 22:52.041
DR. KAREV HERE
IS GOING TO RECOMMEND

22:52.041 --> 22:54.043
SOME WONDERFUL
TREATMENT PROGRAMS FOR YOU.

22:54.043 --> 22:56.546
GO HOME.
GET SOME HELP.

22:56.546 --> 22:57.907
YOU CAN'T JUST DO THAT!

22:57.907 --> 22:59.979
HE JUST DID, MY FRIEND.

23:01.411 --> 23:03.513
OKAY, ANY LUCK YET?

23:03.513 --> 23:04.984
NADA.

23:04.984 --> 23:07.857
UGH. LOOKS LIKE YOU'RE GONNA
HAVE TO SPEND ANOTHER NIGHT.

23:07.857 --> 23:11.491
I HATE TO MISS
THE PARTY.

23:11.491 --> 23:12.722
YOU GONNA MAKE IT?

23:12.722 --> 23:14.894
YOU ARE THE LAST PERSON
ON MY LIST,

23:14.894 --> 23:16.526
SO IT'S LOOKING
PRETTY GOOD.

23:16.526 --> 23:19.429
SO, DOCTORS HAVE LIVES
AFTER ALL. WHO'D HAVE THUNK?

23:19.429 --> 23:22.872
DR. STEVENS,
DISCHARGE MY GUY IN 342.

23:25.605 --> 23:27.807
DON'T LOOK AT ME
LIKE THAT.

23:27.807 --> 23:30.540
IT'S NOT GONNA TAKE
VERY LONG.

23:30.540 --> 23:31.541
IT'S NOT.

23:36.085 --> 23:37.747
YOU PAGE ME?
I'M GONNA BE A WHILE.

23:37.747 --> 23:40.419
DO YOU THINK YOU COULD GET HOME
TO SIGN FOR THE BEER?

23:40.419 --> 23:43.593
WHY DON'T YOU HAVE
YOUR BOYFRIEND SIGN FOR IT?

23:43.593 --> 23:46.756
YOU HAVE A VERY ANNOYING WAY
OF SNEAKING UP ON PEOPLE.

23:46.756 --> 23:49.559
MAYBE IF YOU WERE
A LITTLE LESS CREEPY...

23:49.559 --> 23:51.531
I WOULDN'T COME ANYWAY.
I HATE BIG PARTIES.

23:51.531 --> 23:52.962
IS MEREDITH THE ONLY PERSON

23:52.962 --> 23:55.164
WHO DOESN'T KNOW
THE SIZE OF THIS THING?

23:55.164 --> 23:56.606
I'M TELLING HER.

23:56.606 --> 23:58.568
YOU CAN'T.
SHE'S GONE ALREADY.

23:58.568 --> 23:59.769
WHAT, ALREADY?

23:59.769 --> 24:02.041
I THINK SHE HAD --
UM, EXCUSE ME --

24:02.041 --> 24:03.573
AN ERRAND TO RUN.

24:03.573 --> 24:06.816
YOU DON'T THINK MEREDITH'S
GOING TO MIND, RIGHT?

24:06.816 --> 24:09.078
I WANT YOU TO MAKE IT
VERY CLEAR TO HER

24:09.078 --> 24:11.951
THAT I HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH THIS PARTY -- NOTHING.

24:23.493 --> 24:25.665
OH, I'M SORRY I'M LATE.
IT WAS THE TRAFFIC.

24:25.665 --> 24:26.966
IT DOESN'T MATTER, DEAR.

24:26.966 --> 24:29.539
OKAY. DON'T TELL ME
THE NOTARY DIDN'T SHOW.

24:29.539 --> 24:32.001
OH, EVERYBODY'S HERE.
IT'S JUST YOUR MOTHER ISN'T.

24:33.643 --> 24:34.674
MOM?

24:34.674 --> 24:35.675
MOM?

24:35.675 --> 24:38.107
WHAT DO YOU PEOPLE WANT
FROM ME?

24:38.107 --> 24:40.510
WE NEED YOU TO SIGN
THE LAWYER'S PAPERS.

24:40.510 --> 24:43.553
I HAVE A CRANIAL RECONSTRUCTION
IN A HALF AN HOUR. I NEED TO GO.

24:43.553 --> 24:46.756
OKAY, MOM. WE'RE ALL HERE.
WE HAVE A NOTARY.

24:46.756 --> 24:51.621
I NEED YOU TO FOCUS, AND I NEED
YOU TO SIGN THESE PAPERS.

24:51.621 --> 24:53.893
MOM, LOOK AT ME.

24:53.893 --> 24:55.865
IT'S AN EMERGENCY SURGERY.

24:55.865 --> 24:58.067
I DON'T HAVE TIME
FOR THIS.

24:58.067 --> 24:59.729
SHE CAN'T SIGN
ANYTHING NOW.

24:59.729 --> 25:02.031
WE SHOULD HAVE DONE THIS
EARLIER IN THE DAY.

25:02.031 --> 25:04.203
I COULDN'T COME
EARLIER IN THE DAY.

25:04.203 --> 25:06.736
I HAVE A JOB AND A LIFE,
AND I'M HERE NOW.

25:06.736 --> 25:10.039
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO COME BACK
TOMORROW, WHEN SHE'S LUCID.

25:10.039 --> 25:12.712
YOU KNOW, WHY DID SHE
PUT THIS OFF FOR SO LONG?

25:12.712 --> 25:14.984
AND WHY DID YOU LET HER?

25:14.984 --> 25:17.086
DOESN'T IT STRIKE YOU
AS SLIGHTLY IRRESPONSIBLE?

25:17.086 --> 25:19.949
I MEAN, WHAT THE HELL
IS WRONG WITH YOU PEOPLE?!

25:21.951 --> 25:25.024
Woman:
DR. LEWIS TO PEDS I.C.U.

25:25.024 --> 25:27.196
DR. LEWIS TO PEDS I.C.U.

25:33.763 --> 25:35.264
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

26:34.864 --> 26:37.797
[ DANCE MUSIC PLAYING ]

26:45.604 --> 26:48.007
IZZIE, I'M GONNA KILL YOU.

26:54.784 --> 26:58.818
YOU COULD TOUCH THAT,
BUT I'D HAVE TO KILL YOU.

26:58.818 --> 27:01.050
â™ª AFTER THE SHOW â™ª

27:01.050 --> 27:03.122
â™ª AFTER YOU GO â™ª

27:03.122 --> 27:05.024
SO,
ABOUT THAT TOWEL THING?

27:05.024 --> 27:06.756
IT'S BEEN TAKEN CARE OF.

27:06.756 --> 27:07.857
OKAY.

27:07.857 --> 27:10.099
YOU DON'T NEED
TO CONCERN YOURSELF WITH IT.

27:10.099 --> 27:11.761
SO, WHAT'S GONNA HAPPEN?

27:11.761 --> 27:13.903
WE'RE NOT GONNA
TALK ABOUT IT ANYMORE

27:13.903 --> 27:16.135
IS WHAT'S GONNA HAPPEN --
WE CLEAR?

27:16.135 --> 27:18.868
OR YOU HAD TOO MUCH ALCOHOL
TO UNDERSTAND ME?

27:18.868 --> 27:20.369
WE'RE VERY CLEAR.

27:20.369 --> 27:21.370
GOOD.

27:21.370 --> 27:23.973
YOU HAVE ANY BOURBON?

27:31.380 --> 27:33.282
YOU CAN'T DISCHARGE
A MAN IN PAIN.

27:33.282 --> 27:34.854
OW!
YOU'RE HURTING ME!

27:34.854 --> 27:37.757
YOU'RE THE ONE WHO'S MAKING IT
DIFFICULT. STOP RESISTING.

27:37.757 --> 27:39.358
JUST GIVE ME
THE HIT OF DEMEROL.

27:39.358 --> 27:42.361
THE DILAUDID
HASN'T WORN OFF YET.

27:42.361 --> 27:43.893
LOOK, I'M NOT LEAVING.

27:43.893 --> 27:45.865
I'M CALLING PSYCH.
NO, NO.

27:45.865 --> 27:47.867
DON'T CALL PSYCH.

27:47.867 --> 27:48.838
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

27:48.838 --> 27:50.369
STOP, JERRY.
STOP. STOP. STOP.

27:50.369 --> 27:52.171
[ GASPS ]

27:54.874 --> 27:56.075
JERRY.

27:56.075 --> 27:57.246
JERRY!

27:57.246 --> 27:59.248
CONCUSSION?

28:01.951 --> 28:03.813
